Research (ISPOR). Published by Elsevier Inc. All rights reserved.

DOI: 10.1016/j.jval.2017.04.020
PMID: 28964441 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


369. Value Health. 2017 Sep;20(8):1100-1109. doi: 10.1016/j.jval.2017.04.012.
