Research (ISPOR). Published by Elsevier Inc. All rights reserved.

DOI: 10.1016/j.jval.2017.04.012
PMID: 28964442 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


370. Value Health. 2017 Sep;20(8):1110-1120. doi: 10.1016/j.jval.2017.05.003.
